  "title": {
   "en": "Fukigen na Koushaku-sama wa Uso Hakkenki Tsuki Reijou no Torisetsu wo Goshomou desu"
  },
  "altTitles": [
   {
    "ja": "不機嫌な公爵様はウソ発見器付き令嬢の取説をご所望です"
   },
   {
    "en": "The Grumpy Duke Desires an Instruction Manual for the Lie-Detector Lady"
   }
  ],
  "description": {
   "en": "Countess’s daughter, Ophelia, has a special ability to detect lies. Because of this ability, she lived in seclusion, unable to interact with others. One day, to catch a glimpse of her admired Duke, Claudio, Ophelia participates in a soirée she dislikes. There, she reacts to the conversation filled with noble flattery, trembling and collapsing at the venue... In her haste to leave, she catches the suspicious eye of Claudio, who begins to watch her closely—?",
   "ja": "伯爵令嬢オフィーリアには、「嘘がわかる」という特殊能力がある。その能力ゆえに、人付き合いができずに引きこもって暮らしていた。ある日、憧れの公爵・クラウディオを一目見るため苦手な夜会に参加したオフィーリアは、貴族の?ばかりの会話に反応し会場で震え転げてしまう…。急いでその場を立ち去るも、様子を怪しんだクラウディオに目をつけられてしまい――?"
  },
